with source  $GNOME_URL sources/libcroco/${VERSION:0:3}/libcroco-$VERSION.tar.xz
with info    last 20121031
with info    home http://www.gnome.org/
with info    cite 'CSS parsing library
libcroco is a general CSS parsing and manipulation 
library written in C for the Gnome project.
It provides a CSS2 parser, a CSS2 selection 
engine, and an XML/CSS rendering engine.'
